name: MTD WO Trade Water Drained
query:
select re.name as "Reconciliation:Link/Stock Reconciliation:200",re.posting_date as "Date:Date:100",itm.item_name as "Item:Data:200",ABS(itm.quantity_difference) as "Qty:Float:100" 
from `tabStock Reconciliation` re left join `tabStock Reconciliation Item`  itm on itm.parent = re.name 
where re.docstatus=1 and   re.company='Dure Oil Middle East Factory - Sole Proprietorship LLC' and  re.purpose='Stock Reconciliation' and itm.quantity_difference<0
and itm.item_code ='wo005' and YEAR(re.posting_date) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE()) and MONTH(re.posting_date) = MONTH(CURRENT_DATE())
